    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>在敌对的世界中生存并防守</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个残酷的世界中建造、连接并强化你的基地和Xeno站点。每一个前哨都是你的生命线 - 全力防守，否则将面临彻底毁灭。生存不是赐予的，而是靠一座座建筑争取来的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/0aeb7ae72a2c39c9d49854b2be075bfb.poster.avif?t=1767459485\" width=700 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/0aeb7ae72a2c39c9d49854b2be075bfb.webm?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/0aeb7ae72a2c39c9d49854b2be075bfb.mp4?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>建造多样化的炮塔与战术结构</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个残暴的外星世界中搭建、连接并加固你的基地和Xeno站点。每一个据点都至关重要 - 失去一个，整个防线都可能崩溃。想要活下去，就必须精明建造，稳住前线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/32bace28cfd483b647fb99a229699fe8.poster.avif?t=1767459485\" width=700 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/32bace28cfd483b647fb99a229699fe8.webm?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/32bace28cfd483b647fb99a229699fe8.mp4?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>合作多人模式</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最多4名精英成员并肩作战，对抗威胁你世界的无情敌人。制定战术、灵活应变、释放混乱，守护属于你的一切。每一名队友都不可或缺 - 团队越强，火力越凶猛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/d9cfe61d6273d1e9d1029fb60d078add.poster.avif?t=1767459485\" width=700 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/d9cfe61d6273d1e9d1029fb60d078add.webm?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/d9cfe61d6273d1e9d1029fb60d078add.mp4?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>搜刮以求生存</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜集关键资源，打造强力装备，为即将到来的战斗升级你的配置。每一种材料都至关重要 - 探索得越深入，奖励就越稀有。高风险区域隐藏着最独特的发现，但只有勇敢者才能活着返回。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/d7180012a15bee8b11e5329b6035b48a.poster.avif?t=1767459485\" width=700 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/d7180012a15bee8b11e5329b6035b48a.webm?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/d7180012a15bee8b11e5329b6035b48a.mp4?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>打造你的终极配置</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集资源、制作强化组件并升级你的Scar-X - 这是你在战斗中的主武器，也是最后的生命线。为其装备专用配件，提升射速、威力和操控性，将其打造成真正的毁灭利器。强化建筑以支援前线作战，为你的队伍争取决定性优势。提升Xenite等级可解锁强大的支援模块，足以扭转任何战局。每一次升级，都是为了生存 - 以及统治。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/a8ac69dff233eb3edc7cb2b1b099f41c.poster.avif?t=1767459485\" width=700 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/a8ac69dff233eb3edc7cb2b1b099f41c.webm?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147620/extras/a8ac69dff233eb3edc7cb2b1b099f41c.mp4?t=1767459485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否揭开星球隐藏的秘密，与未知存在结成同盟，并在 <strong>Solitary Horizons</strong> 中延续你种族的遗产？宇宙正等待你的抉择。世界，等待你去探索。</p>",
